net.sf.saxon.charcode
Interface PluggableCharacterSet

All Superinterfaces:
CharacterSet
All Known Implementing Classes:
EucKRCharacterSet, GB2312CharacterSet
public interface PluggableCharacterSet
extends CharacterSet

This interface defines properties of a pluggable character set, that is, a user-supplied character set. This is selected in xsl:output using encoding.XXX="class-name", where XXX is the name of the encoding as used in the encoding property, and class-name is the full name of an implementation of PluggableCharacterSet
